      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement and precise gear selection. The chassis is equipped with a Variable M Differential Lock and original suspension geometry that maintains the model's hallmark communicative steering. Preventative maintenance is addressed, including a VANOS overhaul and rear subframe inspection, ensuring the structural integrity and performance of the platform. The exterior and interior reflect careful ownership, showing only minor patina expected of a well-maintained driver's car.",
